</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-147_"><b>Inclusion</b> - Inclusion involves creating environments where all individuals, regardless of their neurodiversity or other differences, feel welcome, respected, and valued. It's about fostering a sense of belonging and ensuring that everyone has equal opportunities to participate and contribute.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-149_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-150_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cZMNgc bNHzPH pf-151_">Key facts and statistics
