</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-184_">This may involve providing accommodations, offering neurodiversity training for staff, and promoting a culture of acceptance and support.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-186_">Resources like Neurodiversity in the Workplace provide guidance and support for employers in creating inclusive workplaces.
